# ⚙️ CareerForge AI V2 — AI Pipeline Module Specification

## Complete Module Architecture with Dependencies & Data Flow

> **Purpose**: Define EXACTLY what each AI module does, its inputs, outputs, and dependencies
> **No code, no implementation steps** — only module contracts and data flow

