## 🔄 Complete Pipeline Execution Order

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  BUILD ORDER            EXECUTION ORDER (per resume)            │
│                                                                 │
│  1. M1 (Role Mapping)   ──→  Done once during setup            │
│  2. M2 (Preprocessing)  ──→  Step 1: Clean text                │
│  3. M3 (Features)       ──→  Step 2: Extract features          │
│  4. M4 (Role) ═══╗      ──→  Step 3: Predict role              │
│  4. M5 (Skills)══╝      ──→  Step 3: Extract skills (parallel) │
│  5. M6 (Scoring)        ──→  Step 4: Calculate score           │
│  6. M7 (Risk) ═══╗      ──→  Step 5: Predict risk              │
│  6. M8 (Match)═══╝      ──→  Step 5: Match JDs (parallel)     │
│  7. M9 (Trajectory)     ──→  Step 6: Career prediction         │
│  8. M10 (Simulator)     ──→  Step 7: Ready for simulation      │
│  9. M11 (XAI)           ──→  Step 8: Generate explanations     │
│ 10. M12 (Storage)       ──→  Step 9: Persist everything        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

